{"tid":1613113,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[國際文宣] 10月3號夜晚8點 LOL香港隊比賽時上Twitch向外國人宣傳","createTime":"2019-10-02T12:38:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-03T15:45:29.000Z","uid":109780,"like":54,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"f7aed7f14384637411a8a6ee7fc30824bf48a4b0","tid":1613113,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:38:00.000Z","msg":"首先想講唔好驚咩外國人反感<br />\n<strong>Pewdiepie fans</strong>上年都係<strong>50幾萬人</strong>睇緊決賽時，洗頻<strong>SUB TO PEWDIEPIE</strong>，以突顯對私人企業youtube買sub既不滿，行動係成功既<br />\n<br />\n聽晚(3/10)有香港隊HKA既比賽，我唔理佢地老闆鍾培生親共親成點<br />\n但聽日比賽至少有<strong>10萬人</strong>睇，加埋台灣既<strong>2萬</strong>人，係一個唔錯既國際文宣平台<br />\n下面係今日比賽既觀看人數，聽日HKA比賽時台灣會有更多人睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yUvwp6o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUvwp6o.png&h=c6789912&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有Twitch AC既全部同我準備好，冇ac既而家即刻同我開返個，開ac link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2F&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=a5e4c6a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/</a><br />\n<br />\n行動會係8點開始，但因為比賽時間會因上一場既結束時間而不穩定<br />\n<strong>請7點45分準備好</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n凌晨12點都有場，參唔參與自己決定 (香港人邊有咁早訓啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VmhiPzs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVmhiPzs.jpg&h=382965e8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n英文台link: <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/riotgames\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Friotgames&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=039ee040\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/riotgames</a><br />\n中文台link: <a href=\"https://www.twitch.tv/garenatw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitch.tv%2Fgarenatw&d=Bbcm6JBZsUbsJrWfDZmHX5wtdbXJE8TYY9MHUmPwwUI%3D&h=cdf0fc91\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.twitch.tv/garenatw</a><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命<br />\n五大訴命，缺一不可<br />\n香港人加油"},{"pid":"2cbe7f187054e57e5bb2e02d0b537c5b51ea83b2","tid":1613113,"uid":190141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"鐘仔感覺唔算好親共? 612 果陣都有出POST叫大家小心安全之類<br />\n<br />\n不過過左3個月可能都變親未定<br />\n<br />\nBTW順便支持埋HKA 打埋入小組賽既到時再係group stage文宣效果大好多 group一定多人過play in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a17adae9b41f3e3aadec4c656342043e258a52","tid":1613113,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cbe7f187054e57e5bb2e02d0b537c5b51ea83b2","tid":1613113,"uid":190141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"鐘仔感覺唔算好親共? 612 果陣都有出POST叫大家小心安全之類<br />\n<br />\n不過過左3個月可能都變親未定<br />\n<br />\nBTW順便支持埋HKA 打埋入小組賽既到時再係group stage文宣效果大好多 group一定多人過play in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:41:07.000Z","msg":"今次一定要支持HKA，入到小組賽又可以再文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e15d11b6de1d4357947e5763c10f48bddd2bb890","tid":1613113,"uid":190141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71a17adae9b41f3e3aadec4c656342043e258a52","tid":1613113,"uid":109780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cbe7f187054e57e5bb2e02d0b537c5b51ea83b2","tid":1613113,"uid":190141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T12:39:49.000Z","msg":"鐘仔感覺唔算好親共? 612 果陣都有出POST叫大家小心安全之類<br />\n<br />\n不過過左3個月可能都變親未定<br />\n<br />\nBTW順便支持埋HKA 打埋入小組賽既到時再係group stage文宣效果大好多 group一定多人過play in<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" c